Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.84,0:00:01.96,Default,,0,0,0,,《法外情真》前情回顾\N{\fs12}Previously on The Guardian
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.96,0:00:03.96,Default,,0,0,0,,我有动脉堵塞了\N{\fs12}I've got a little blockage...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.96,0:00:05.36,Default,,0,0,0,,五条动脉里堵了四条\N{\fs12}four out of five arterial.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.36,0:00:06.38,Default,,0,0,0,,那你需要手术吗\N{\fs12}So you need surgery?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.38,0:00:08.06,Default,,0,0,0,,露露怀孕了\N{\fs12}Lulu's pregnant, and...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.06,0:00:10.06,Default,,0,0,0,,我只是希望你能陪伴\N{\fs12}I just hope that you'd be around to be there...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.06,0:00:10.82,Default,,0,0,0,,在你孙儿的身边\N{\fs12}for your grand kids.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.44,0:00:15.94,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道我已经做好了当爸爸的准备\N{\fs12}I know that I'm ready to be a father.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.94,0:00:18.22,Default,,0,0,0,,我不想结婚就只是因为我怀孕了\N{\fs12}I don't want to get married just because I'm pregnant.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.44,0:00:20.22,Default,,0,0,0,,我喜欢你\N{\fs12}I like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.46,0:00:21.80,Default,,0,0,0,,当我有所心动的时候\N{\fs12}When I feel something...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.20,0:00:23.80,Default,,0,0,0,,我希望能全心而动\N{\fs12}I like to feel it.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.88,0:00:29.84,Default,,0,0,0,,能不能给我来一杯龙舌兰酒\N{\fs12}Can I get a shot of Tequila?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.43,0:01:16.94,Default,,0,0,0,,911紧急呼叫\N{\fs12}911 Emergency.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.06,0:01:19.14,Default,,0,0,0,,这儿有一个拿着枪的男人在对人开枪\N{\fs12}There's a man with a gun,and he's shooting people.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.26,0:01:20.64,Default,,0,0,0,,你在哪儿  女士\N{\fs12}Where are you, ma'am?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.76,0:01:22.68,Default,,0,0,0,,凯恩工业\N{\fs12}Kane Industry.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.81,0:01:24.40,Default,,0,0,0,,是凯恩实业公司吗  对吗  女士\N{\fs12}Kane Industries?Js that what you said, ma'am?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.53,0:01:26.22,Default,,0,0,0,,噢  天呐\N{\fs12}Oh, God!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.35,0:01:27.88,Default,,0,0,0,,女士  你还在那儿吗\N{\fs12}Ma'am? You're at Kane Industries?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.01,0:01:29.54,Default,,0,0,0,,他刚才又射中一个人\N{\fs12}He just shot someone else.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.61,0:01:31.07,Default,,0,0,0,,你在哪一层  女士\N{\fs12}What floor are you on, ma'am?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.20,0:01:34.08,Default,,0,0,0,,他正在房间里走  他在四处查看  我不能说话\N{\fs12}He's walking down the room. He's looking around. J can't talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.96,0:01:38.10,Default,,0,0,0,,你还在在吗  有人吗\N{\fs12}Are you there? Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.22,0:01:40.11,Default,,0,0,0,,他刚才射中了他自己\N{\fs12}He just shot himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.23,0:01:43.30,Default,,0,0,0,,结束了  他对自己开了枪\N{\fs12}lt's over. He just shot himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.43,0:01:45.31,Default,,0,0,0,,- 早啊  格雷琴  - 早啊  法林先生\N{\fs12}- Morning, Gretchen.- Good morning, Mr. Fallin.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.44,0:01:48.66,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你好啊  - 需要我帮您拿公文包吗\N{\fs12}- How are you?- Can I help you with your briefcase?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.79,0:01:50.39,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我的公文包吗  - 对\N{\fs12}- My briefcase?- Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.51,0:01:52.21,Default,,0,0,0,,不用了  我能自己拿  谢谢\N{\fs12}No, I can handle it, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.33,0:01:54.28,Default,,0,0,0,,我要拿一杯黑咖啡  谢谢  不过\N{\fs12}I'll take a black comee, though, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.41,0:01:56.83,Default,,0,0,0,,加奶油和两块糖  行吧\N{\fs12}Make it cream and two sugars, all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.96,0:01:58.33,Default,,0,0,0,,好\N{\fs12}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.54,0:02:01.21,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿  伯顿  你今天感觉怎么样\N{\fs12}Hey, Burton, how are you feeling today?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.33,0:02:02.96,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿  杰克  你怎么样  我挺好的  谢了\N{\fs12}Hey, Jake, how you doing? I'm good, thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.09,0:02:07.98,Default,,0,0,0,,好  好  听着  我恐怕要带一些很糟糕的消息给你了\N{\fs12}Good. Good. Listen, I'm afraid I've got some very bad news for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.90,0:02:18.92,Default,,0,0,0,,早\N{\fs12}Morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.05,0:02:21.22,Default,,0,0,0,,噢  尼克  我能跟你聊一下吗\N{\fs12}Oh, Nick, can I talk to you for a second?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.35,0:02:24.61,Default,,0,0,0,,泰德  你能在那儿坐一会儿吗  我马上就来\N{\fs12}Ted, will you just take a seat over there? I'll be right with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.12,0:02:36.89,Default,,0,0,0,,那个男孩的父亲  今天上午在凯恩纸业射中了三个人\N{\fs12}That kid Ted's father shot three people at Kane Paper this morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.02,0:02:38.97,Default,,0,0,0,,什么\N{\fs12}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.42,0:02:48.48,Default,,0,0,0,,其中的两个人已经死了  而且他的父亲开枪打了他自己\N{\fs12}Two of them are dead, and his father shot himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.61,0:02:51.45,Default,,0,0,0,,孩子不知道吗\N{\fs12}He doesn't know?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.66,0:02:54.22,Default,,0,0,0,,不知道\N{\fs12}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.54,0:03:52.53,Default,,0,0,0,,我为什么在这儿\N{\fs12}Why am I here?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.65,0:03:55.54,Default,,0,0,0,,泰德  这位女士是来自社区服务中心的\N{\fs12}Ted, there's this woman from Social Services,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.67,0:03:57.14,Default,,0,0,0,,她有些话必须和你说  所以\N{\fs12}and she has to talk to you, so--
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.27,0:03:59.23,Default,,0,0,0,,可以  但是我为什么在这里\N{\fs12}Okay, but why am I here?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.78,0:04:06.57,Default,,0,0,0,,嗨  泰德  我是苏珊娜\N{\fs12}Hi, Ted. I'm Suzanne.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.70,0:04:09.68,Default,,0,0,0,,贝尔纳教练  你在这儿做什么\N{\fs12}Coach Bernardo? What are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.80,0:04:11.15,Default,,0,0,0,,就是  呃\N{\fs12}Just, uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.28,0:04:14.23,Default,,0,0,0,,就是看看你怎么样了  孩子\N{\fs12}Just seeing how you're doing, kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.90,0:04:18.37,Default,,0,0,0,,泰德  你的父亲卷入到了一起事件中\N{\fs12}Ted, there's been an incident involving your father.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.49,0:04:19.97,Default,,0,0,0,,什么\N{\fs12}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.10,0:04:23.14,Default,,0,0,0,,他受伤了  医生们正在尽力抢救他\N{\fs12}He's been hurt, and the doctors are trying to help him.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.20,0:04:25.55,Default,,0,0,0,,那  发生了什么\N{\fs12}Well, what happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.21,0:04:31.58,Default,,0,0,0,,他走了进去  还和一些人打了招呼\N{\fs12}He walked in, and he said hello to a few people.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.70,0:04:33.92,Default,,0,0,0,,然后他走向了凯恩先生\N{\fs12}And then he walked right up to Mr. Kane.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.04,0:04:37.22,Default,,0,0,0,,拔出了一把枪  然后他\N{\fs12}And he pulled out a gun, and he just...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.34,0:04:39.08,Default,,0,0,0,,大家为了在那儿开晨会\N{\fs12}Everyone was there for the morning meeting,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.20,0:04:41.19,Default,,0,0,0,,他朝着凯恩先生的头就开枪了\N{\fs12}and he just shot Mr. Kane in the head.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.32,0:04:45.04,Default,,0,0,0,,然后他射中了珍妮  射中了文斯\N{\fs12}And then he shot Jenny and then he shot Vince.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.17,0:04:47.09,Default,,0,0,0,,而且他对文斯开了三枪\N{\fs12}And he shot Vince three times.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.22,0:04:49.66,Default,,0,0,0,,我很抱歉  安妮特\N{\fs12}I'm so sorry, Annette.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.78,0:04:52.32,Default,,0,0,0,,呃  你想和比尔·詹姆森谈谈  是吗\N{\fs12}Um, you wanted to talk to Bill Jameson, right,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.44,0:04:53.86,Default,,0,0,0,,是关于他这次对新闻界的声明吗\N{\fs12}about his statement for the press?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.98,0:04:57.22,Default,,0,0,0,,对  出于法律的原因我们说话不得不谨慎一点\N{\fs12}Right. We have to be a little careful what we say, legal reasons.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.35,0:05:01.52,Default,,0,0,0,,听着  安妮特  如果你有任何的其他问题\N{\fs12}Listen, Annette, if you have any more problems,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.64,0:05:03.67,Default,,0,0,0,,只要你需要  随时打我电话\N{\fs12}you need anything at all, just call me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.79,0:05:05.40,Default,,0,0,0,,这是个直线电话  好吗\N{\fs12}This is a direct number, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.52,0:05:06.71,Default,,0,0,0,,好\N{\fs12}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.84,0:05:09.40,Default,,0,0,0,,好了  坚持下去\N{\fs12}All right. Hang in there.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.53,0:05:11.17,Default,,0,0,0,,- 好吗  - 好的\N{\fs12}- All right? - All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.29,0:05:13.22,Default,,0,0,0,,- 谢谢你  - 保重保重\N{\fs12}- Thank you. - Take care.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.84,0:05:55.02,Default,,0,0,0,,埃里克\N{\fs12}Eric?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.63,0:05:58.17,Default,,0,0,0,,伯顿  嘿\N{\fs12}Burton, hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.29,0:06:00.25,Default,,0,0,0,,还好吗  孩子\N{\fs12}How you doing, son?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.38,0:06:01.50,Default,,0,0,0,,我还好\N{\fs12}I'm good.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.63,0:06:04.23,Default,,0,0,0,,你父亲的事我感到很抱歉\N{\fs12}I'm so sorry to hear about your dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.35,0:06:07.14,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你什么时候来的  - 我刚到这儿\N{\fs12}- When did you get here? - I just got here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.27,0:06:09.07,Default,,0,0,0,,你感觉怎么样\N{\fs12}How are you feeling?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.19,0:06:11.09,Default,,0,0,0,,噢  我  我不错\N{\fs12}Oh, I'm--I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.21,0:06:13.72,Default,,0,0,0,,我听说那个心脏手术了  那挺严重的\N{\fs12}I heard about the heart surgery. That's some serious stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.84,0:06:15.32,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯  我现在挺好的\N{\fs12}Well, now I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.44,0:06:16.95,Default,,0,0,0,,很难相信你已经可以起来走动了\N{\fs12}Hard to believe you're already up and around.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.02,0:06:20.51,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊  我没事  谢谢你  你还能撑住吗\N{\fs12}No. I'm fine, thank you. But how are you holding up?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.64,0:06:22.15,Default,,0,0,0,,我可以的\N{\fs12}I'm good.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.27,0:06:25.74,Default,,0,0,0,,你不觉得你需要  呃  回家或者\N{\fs12}You don't think maybe you should, uh... be back at home or--
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.86,0:06:28.94,Default,,0,0,0,,我没事了  已经  我  呃\N{\fs12}I'm good, really. l, uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.07,0:06:31.44,Default,,0,0,0,,我已经准备好和大家谈了  所以\N{\fs12}I already talked to everybody, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.57,0:06:33.53,Default,,0,0,0,,噢\N{\fs12}Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.65,0:06:37.18,Default,,0,0,0,,好  听好  如果你妈妈需要什么\N{\fs12}Well, listen, if your mom needs anything,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.31,0:06:39.88,Default,,0,0,0,,帮忙葬礼的事  或者其他一些事情  你要让我知道好吗\N{\fs12}any help with the funeral or anything else, will you let me know?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.00,0:06:42.25,Default,,0,0,0,,伯顿\N{\fs12}Burton...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.88,0:06:46.77,Default,,0,0,0,,我想完成和帕拉马尔的交易\N{\fs12}I want to finish the Palamar deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.89,0:06:48.50,Default,,0,0,0,,这事儿比较急\N{\fs12}There's a clock on this thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.66,0:06:55.68,Default,,0,0,0,,你现在不用担心交易的事\N{\fs12}You don't have to worry about that right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.81,0:06:57.22,Default,,0,0,0,,我是说  我们可以延长这件事的时间\N{\fs12}I mean, we can get that extended.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.35,0:07:01.45,Default,,0,0,0,,我想尽快召集董事会\N{\fs12}I want to assemble the board as soon as possible
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.58,0:07:04.37,Default,,0,0,0,,让他们批准我担任执行总裁\N{\fs12}and have them approve me as CEO.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.42,0:07:10.27,Default,,0,0,0,,那  我觉得如果你休息一段时间会更好\N{\fs12}Well, I was thinking maybe it'd be a good idea if you took a little time off.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.40,0:07:12.77,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道  我父亲为了这个单子已经忙了五年了\N{\fs12}You know, my father's been working on this deal for five years.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.90,0:07:14.63,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我明白  - 所以你去安排和董事们开个会\N{\fs12}- I understand. - So you'll get a meeting with the board.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.69,0:07:19.44,Default,,0,0,0,,好  我  我可能\N{\fs12}Well, l--l probably--
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.56,0:07:21.74,Default,,0,0,0,,好  谢谢\N{\fs12}Good! Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.99,0:07:23.89,Default,,0,0,0,,好\N{\fs12}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.02,0:07:25.78,Default,,0,0,0,,那\N{\fs12}Well--
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.91,0:07:27.23,Default,,0,0,0,,打扰一下\N{\fs12}Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.35,0:07:29.28,Default,,0,0,0,,埃里克  这是约拿·西尔弗曼医生\N{\fs12}Eric, this is Dr. Jonah Silverman.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.41,0:07:31.20,Default,,0,0,0,,他是一名心理学家  他想和你聊聊\N{\fs12}He's a psychologist, and he'd like to talk to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.33,0:07:32.23,Default,,0,0,0,,你好\N{\fs12}Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.35,0:07:33.86,Default,,0,0,0,,感谢您的到来  西尔弗曼医生\N{\fs12}Appreciate you coming down, Dr. Silverman,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.99,0:07:36.27,Default,,0,0,0,,但是我现在非常忙\N{\fs12}but I'm very busy right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.39,0:07:37.68,Default,,0,0,0,,呃  埃里克\N{\fs12}Uh, Eric--
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.80,0:07:39.63,Default,,0,0,0,,安妮特  也许我们可以把和西尔弗曼医生见面\N{\fs12}Annette, perhaps we can meet with Dr. Silverman
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.76,0:07:41.14,Default,,0,0,0,,的时候更好的安排在我的日程表上\N{\fs12}when it works better for my schedule.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.27,0:07:45.09,Default,,0,0,0,,当然  当然  等你准备好了再找我\N{\fs12}Sure. Sure. Call me when you're ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.88,0:07:54.03,Default,,0,0,0,,好  呃  保重\N{\fs12}Well, take, uh... take care.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.36,0:08:14.96,Default,,0,0,0,,他射中了三个人吗\N{\fs12}He shot three people?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.09,0:08:17.94,Default,,0,0,0,,很显然  是的\N{\fs12}Apparently, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.07,0:08:21.70,Default,,0,0,0,,泰德  我们现在需要了解一些关于你\N{\fs12}Ted, part of what we need to do right now is Iearn a little bit about you,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.82,0:08:24.48,Default,,0,0,0,,和你们父子之间关系的事\N{\fs12}about your relationship with your father.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.61,0:08:25.61,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么\N{\fs12}Why?
