Dialogue: 0,0:37:12.78,0:37:15.72,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你听说了吗  - 什么\N{\fs12}- You heard? - What?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:17.96,0:37:19.40,Default,,0,0,0,,休伯蒂死了\N{\fs12}Huberty's dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:19.52,0:37:20.87,Default,,0,0,0,,- 对  - 对\N{\fs12}- Right. - Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:20.99,0:37:23.52,Default,,0,0,0,,我希望他没少吃苦\N{\fs12}I hope he suffered.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:33.64,0:37:34.83,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿\N{\fs12}Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:37.89,0:37:39.49,Default,,0,0,0,,坐吧  尼古拉斯\N{\fs12}Sit down, Nicholas.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:47.54,0:37:53.43,Default,,0,0,0,,关于昨晚的事  我希望你能理解  那只是一个\N{\fs12}About last night, I hope you understand that it was just a...
Dialogue: 0,0:37:56.33,0:37:58.15,Default,,0,0,0,,- 只是个什么  - 一个失误\N{\fs12}- Just a what? - A mistake.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:58.28,0:37:59.97,Default,,0,0,0,,好  我明白\N{\fs12}Well, I know that.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:00.10,0:38:04.00,Default,,0,0,0,,而且我明白你是在为我冒险\N{\fs12}And I know that you've gone out on a limb for me
Dialogue: 0,0:38:04.12,0:38:06.14,Default,,0,0,0,,为了执行合伙人的事\N{\fs12}with this managing partner thing,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:06.27,0:38:08.28,Default,,0,0,0,,我想让你知道  我不想让你失望\N{\fs12}and I want you to know that I will not let you down.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:09.87,0:38:12.43,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧  我认为这对其他的合伙人相当不公平\N{\fs12}Well, I don't think it's quite fair to the other partners.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:12.56,0:38:14.19,Default,,0,0,0,,你什么意思\N{\fs12}What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:14.32,0:38:18.31,Default,,0,0,0,,这是他们养家糊口的活儿  尼古拉斯  他们一辈子的事业\N{\fs12}This is their livelihood, Nicholas. Their life's work.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:18.44,0:38:20.48,Default,,0,0,0,,他们必须得有一个负责任的领导人\N{\fs12}They've gotta be sure their leader is responsible.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:20.61,0:38:22.27,Default,,0,0,0,,我会有责任感的\N{\fs12}I will be responsible.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:30.45,0:38:33.36,Default,,0,0,0,,我现在不能这么做\N{\fs12}I can't do it right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:33.49,0:38:37.20,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉\N{\fs12}I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:37.32,0:38:39.56,Default,,0,0,0,,我不会做的\N{\fs12}I won't do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:59.84,0:39:02.40,Default,,0,0,0,,- 哦  嘿  泰德  - 嘿  教练\N{\fs12}- Oh, hey, Ted. - Hey, Coach.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:02.53,0:39:04.22,Default,,0,0,0,,你为什么不进去  布赖恩和马西正在看电视\N{\fs12}Why don't you come on in? Brian and Marcy are watching TV.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:04.35,0:39:05.79,Default,,0,0,0,,你怎么不和他们出去玩玩呢\N{\fs12}Why don't you hang out with them?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:05.91,0:39:08.09,Default,,0,0,0,,谢了  贝尔纳教练\N{\fs12}Thanks, Coach Bernardo.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:08.21,0:39:11.09,Default,,0,0,0,,- 再见  - 再见  泰德\N{\fs12}- See you. - See you, Ted.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:23.90,0:39:25.53,Default,,0,0,0,,那么\N{\fs12}So...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:25.66,0:39:27.90,Default,,0,0,0,,对\N{\fs12}Yep.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:28.02,0:39:29.43,Default,,0,0,0,,你需要更多的\N{\fs12}Do you need any more...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:29.56,0:39:33.39,Default,,0,0,0,,不用  我可以  目前来说\N{\fs12}No, I'm okay... for now.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:35.47,0:39:37.10,Default,,0,0,0,,你需要什么可以告诉我\N{\fs12}Just let me know what you need.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:37.22,0:39:38.66,Default,,0,0,0,,我会给你开张支票\N{\fs12}I'll write you a check.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:40.32,0:39:42.47,Default,,0,0,0,,- 好  - 好\N{\fs12}- Great. - Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:47.00,0:39:51.61,Default,,0,0,0,,尼古拉斯尊敬地要求  我继续担任执行合伙人\N{\fs12}Nicholas has respectfully requested that I stay on as managing partner,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:51.73,0:39:54.51,Default,,0,0,0,,在目前的这段时间\N{\fs12}at least for the time being.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:54.64,0:39:58.35,Default,,0,0,0,,我私底下猜想过  他可能就是不想每天和老男人一起打高尔夫\N{\fs12}I privately suspect that he just doesn't want the old man playing golf every day.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:00.90,0:40:03.74,Default,,0,0,0,,现在我很高兴的宣布我们公司的收益\N{\fs12}Now I'm pleased to announce that our corporate revenue
Dialogue: 0,0:40:03.87,0:40:06.81,Default,,0,0,0,,在上个季度提高了百分之二十\N{\fs12}went up 20% last last quarter.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:06.94,0:40:11.38,Default,,0,0,0,,而且杰克这儿带了两个非常重要的客户\N{\fs12}And Jake here brought in two very important clients,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:11.51,0:40:15.70,Default,,0,0,0,,皮尔斯控股和哈尔西电子\N{\fs12}the Pierce Holdings and Halsey Electronics.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:15.82,0:40:18.54,Default,,0,0,0,,还有  房地产部门的业绩在上个季度提高了百分之七\N{\fs12}Also, the real estate department went up Iast quarter, 7%.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:18.66,0:40:20.20,Default,,0,0,0,,继续上升  鲍勃  很棒\N{\fs12}Keep that up, Bob. Excellent.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:55.40,0:40:57.29,Default,,0,0,0,,对不起\N{\fs12}I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:02.59,0:41:05.44,Default,,0,0,0,,真的很对不起  露露\N{\fs12}I'm so sorry, Lulu.
